mintWithColla(address,uint256,uint256,ui.details: mint USDs by entering collateral amount (excluding ETH)

params.collateralAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral
params.collateralAmt: the amount of collateral to stake

mintWithEth(uint256,uint256,uint256).details: mint USDs by ETH note: this function needs changes when USDs is deployed on other blockchain platform

mintWithSPA(address,uint256,uint256,uint.details: mint USDs by entering SPA amount

params.SPAamt: the amount of SPA to burn
params.collateralAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

mintWithUSDs(address,uint256,uint256,uin.details: mint USDs by entering USDs amount

params.USDsMintAmt: the amount of USDs to be minted
params.collateralAddr: the address of user's chosen collateral

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

rebase().details: Calculate the total value of collaterals held by the Vault and all      strategies and update the supply of USDs.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updateSwapInFee(bool).details: disable swapInFee, i.e. mint becomes free

updateSwapOutFee(bool).details: disable swapOutFee, i.e. redeem becomes free

allocateAll().notice: Allocate unallocated funds on Vault to strategies.
